Feature: NewsMenu

  In order to see news from different categories
  As a user
  I want to be able to navigate through a menu of categories

  Scenario Outline: NewsCategories
    Given I am on the BBC News website
    When I click on the <category> news category menu item
    Then I get the news under <category>
    Examples:
      | category             |
      | Home                 |
      | Video                |
      | World                |
      | UK                   |
      | Business             |
      | Tech                 |
      | Science              |
      | Magazine             |
      | Entertainment & Arts |
      | Health               |
      | In Pictures          |
